Version 0.4.0 (20/08/2006)
	* Allow to login as different user
	* Code improvements

Version 0.3.6 (17/08/2006)
	* Fixed bug that made tool crash when there is a checked-out file
	* Added progress bars
	* UCMCC - Baseline now shows more information on each baseline
	* Hashing some `cleartool` command output for better performance
	* Views with comments are now handled currectly
	* Views that don't have "View properties:" line in `cleartool lsact -long`
	  will be considered dynamic

Version 0.3.5 (2006-05-30)
	* Fixed duplicated files error

Version 0.3.4 (2006-05-28)
	* Fixed link to QCT CodeCollaborator server

Version 0.3.3 (2006-05-28)
	* Better "Review Done" message
	* Code improvement
	* Fixed hang problem in snapshot-view

Version 0.3.2 (2006-05-15)
	* Explictly call `ccollab set scm clearcase`

Version 0.3.1 (2006-05-15)
	* Fixed bug in activity name finding
	* Added warning about developer branch rebase

Version 0.3.0 (2006-05-07)
	* Getting the "right" base version
	* Added note about "activity lifespan"
	* Flash taskbar when done uploading

Version 0.2.0 (2006-05-04)
	* New UI for `UCMCC - Baseline`
	* Added instructions on how to install and configure `ccollab`
	* Added `Known Bugs` section
	* Add `Installing` section
	* More detailed error messages
	* Allow for space in file names
	* Check for `UCMCC_USER` environment variable

Version 0.1.3 (2006-04-27)
	* Check that `ccollab` is in PATH
	* Add "Prerequisites" section
	* Fixed a bug in finding baseline changes

Version 0.1.2 (2006-04-27)
	* Better detection of view owner

Version 0.1.1 (2006-04-27)
	* Added license (BSD) 
	* Catch more errors (specially on startup)
	* Fixed typo in installer
	* Check that cleartool is in path
	* Better sorting of baselines (by date reversed)

Version 0.1.0 (2006-04-24)
